@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>


<MudGrid>
    
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="12" md="6">
        <MudCard Elevation="10">
            <MudCardHeader>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Align="Align.Justify">
                    <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.MapsHomeWork" Size="Size.Medium"></MudIcon>
                    Welcome To ProERP
                </MudText>
            </MudCardHeader>
            <MudCardContent>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
                    Most ERP systems are bloated, overpriced, and packed with features you’ll never use — yet you still end up paying for them. Big-name providers charge millions for complexity that only makes sense at the enterprise level.
                    <br/><br/>
                    <b>ProERP is different.</b>
                    <br/>
                    Built by a small business for small businesses, it gives you exactly what you need — and nothing you don’t. You choose the modules you want (Inventory, Purchasing, Invoicing, etc.), and only pay for what you use.
                    <br/><br/>
                    <b>No fluff. No hidden fees.</b>
                    <br/>
                    Just a clean, powerful, and affordable ERP system that works the way your business does.
                </MudText>
            </MudCardContent>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>
    
    <MudItem xs="12" sm="12" md="6">
        <MudCard Elevation="10">
            <MudCardHeader>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.h6" Align="Align.Justify">
                    <MudIcon Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.ViewModule" Size="Size.Medium"></MudIcon>
                    ProERP Modules
                </MudText>
            </MudCardHeader>
            <MudCardContent>
                <MudText Typo="Typo.body2">
                    With <b>ProERP</b>, every feature is a module — so you’re never stuck paying for tools you don’t need. Whether it's Inventory Management, Purchase Tracking, Invoicing, or something custom, you pick only the modules that matter to your business.
                    <br/><br/>
                    No massive bundled packages.<br/>
                    No wasted resources.<br/>
                    Just the features you need, when you need them.
                    <br/><br/>
                    This modular approach keeps costs low and value high — giving small businesses the flexibility and control they deserve.

                </MudText>
            </MudCardContent>
        </MudCard>
    </MudItem>
    
    

</MudGrid>

